</messaging:plainTextEmailBody>

<messaging:htmlEmailBody > 


<apex:outputText style="text-transform: capitalize" value="Dear {!relatedTo.RW_Booking__r.Primary_Applicant_Name__c}"></apex:outputText> <apex:outputPanel rendered="{!relatedTo.RW_Applicant2_Name__c != null}"> <apex:outputText value=" and "/><apex:outputText style="text-transform: capitalize" value="{!relatedTo.RW_Applicant2_Name__c}"></apex:outputText></apex:outputPanel>,<br/><br/>

Greetings from {!relatedTo.RW_Project__c}!
<br/><br/>

<!-- The {!relatedTo.RW_Project__c} team congratulates you and thanks you for choosing us for making your home.<br/><br/>-->
Congratulations and welcome to the Runwal family.


Regarding your booking dated <b><apex:outputText value="{0, date, MMM d, yyyy}"> <apex:param value="{!relatedTo.RW_Booking__r.Booking_Date__c}" /> </apex:outputText></b> for Runwal {!relatedTo.RW_Booking__r.Unit_No__r.RW_Param1__c} {!relatedTo.RW_Booking__r.Unit_No__r.RW_Param4__c}, we would like to confirm the details of your unit and provide you with additional important information related to your booking. 
<br/>

    
<p><b><u>Booking Details:</u></b></p>

