For any discrepancies in the above information, please do get in touch with us at the earliest to have the same corrected.

<p><b><u>Funding of your unit:</u></b></p> 

Should you wish to apply for a home loan, you may connect with our in-house home loan expert who is available on <u>{!relatedTo.RW_Booking__r.Project__r.Home_Loan_Email__c}</u>. Alternatively, you may also contact the team on +91-{!relatedTo.RW_Booking__r.Project__r.Home_Loan_Contact_1__c} <apex:outputPanel rendered="{!relatedTo.RW_Booking__r.Project__r.Home_Loan_Contact_2__c!= null}"> <apex:outputText value="/{!relatedTo.RW_Booking__r.Project__r.Home_Loan_Contact_2__c}"/></apex:outputPanel>.<br/><br/>

In case your home loan application is already in progress, request you to please share the sanction letter with us at the earliest for our internal documentation. To avail bank loan, you are required to first make the payment of your own contribution and register your unit.

<p><u><b>Regarding registration of your unit:</b></u></p> 

We would be commencing the process of execution and registration of 'Agreement for Sale' in respect of your captioned booked unit shortly.<br/><br/>

You are requested to fill the attached <b>'Name Confirmation Form'</b> to prepare the Agreement for Sale and send across a signed copy of the same at the earliest.

<br/>

<apex:outputPanel rendered="{!OR(relatedTo.RW_Booking__r.Stamp_duty_payable_by_Runwal__c == 0, relatedTo.RW_Booking__r.Stamp_duty_payable_by_Runwal__c == null)}">
<p><b>The payment details of stamp duty and registration charges are as below:</b></p> 
<br/>


<table class="center" style="border:1px solid black;border-collapse:collapse;text-align:center;">
