<p><b><u>Payment towards your unit:</u></b></p> 

You will be sent a demand letter in accordance with your payment plan and you would be required to pay the dues within the stipulated due date. There are three components to every demand that you will receive – payment towards the unit, payment towards the GST and payment towards the TDS. <br/><br/>

Request you to kindly make your payments on or prior to the due date to avoid any additional charges that get incurred on payments received post due date.

Flat cost payment cheque in favour of “{!relatedTo.RW_Booking__r.Unit_No__r.Legal_Entity__r.Account_Name_Flat_Cost__c}” OR through RTGS/NEFT, the details of which are tabulated below:
