You may also contact Mr. Gourav Mardia at gourav@gyaata.in (+91-9920350878 / +91-9699350878) who can help you with the same. <br/>
<p><b><u>Refer and Earn:</u></b></p> 

We believe our existing customers are our brand ambassadors and we have some very special privileges tailor-made only for you.  

One such initiative is our Referral and Loyalty Program that offers both value added benefits and experiential offerings to its members and their friends and family. Every booking referred by you in any of our projects, entitles your referral to a discount immediately at the time of booking. What’s more, you too in turn earn credits that can be redeemed against your dues towards your own unit. Besides, being a preferred customer gives you access to glittering events and distinctive experiences. 
<br/><br/>
<p><b><u>Contacting Us:</u></b></p>

<!-- We operate out of our CRM office at <b><I>R-City Mall, North Wing, 9th floor, Unit Nos. 3<apex:outputText value="&"/>4, LBS Marg, Ghatkopar West-400086.</I></b> In case you wish to visit us, in the interest of better schedule and time management, it would be appreciated if an appointment with your Relationship Manager is fixed a day in advance so that we can serve you better.<br/><br/>-->
We operate out of our CRM office at <b>{!relatedTo.RW_Booking__r.Project__r.CRM_Office_Address__c}.</b> In case you wish to visit us, in the interest of better schedule and time management, it would be appreciated if an appointment with your Relationship Manager is fixed a day in advance so that we can serve you better.<br/><br/>
We are also reachable on {!relatedTo.RW_Booking__r.Unit_No__r.Relationship_Manager__r.did_number_from_user__c} from 10 AM to 6 PM (except on Sundays, 2nd <apex:outputText value="&"/> 4th Saturdays and statutory holidays).  You are requested to call on this number from your registered mobile number ONLY. It is crucial for you to call from your registered mobile number as that number has been fed into the back-end system to route your call directly to your designated Relationship Manager. If your call is unanswered / missed, then your call will be returned within 1 working day.<br/> <br/>

In our continuous endeavour to bring every convenience to your doorstep, we are pleased to introduce a quick and convenient mode of communication - an exclusive <b><I>Customer Self Service Portal</I></b> and <b><I>R-Connect App</I></b>, specifically created to help you track the details and progress of your home 24X7.  

The <b><I>Customer Self-Service Portal</I></b> and <b><I>R-Connect App</I></b> will showcase details of your unit, your profile and contact details as registered with us, payment history, balances dues and taxes, payment modes to ease your payment transactions, construction updates and also the option to submit your referral leads to enable you to track the status of the same. <br/>

