<br/><br/>-->

A mail with the login details to access your <b><I>Customer Self-Service Portal</I></b> and the <b><I>R-Connect App</I></b> will be sent to you shortly.<br/>

<!--Below is a link that will walk-you through the process of logging in and taking you through the features of the <b><I>Customer Self-Service Portal</I></b> and the <b><I>R-Connect App and various other aspects of your journey with us:</I></b><br/>
<a href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLIpRRatbhQuWdwWP_KF2GXsQynzRJv2i3">link</a>
<br/><br/>-->
For any query you are kindly requested to write to us on {!relatedTo.RW_Booking__r.Project__r.Customer_Care_Email__c} from your registered email ID for us to track and serve you better. 
<br/><br/>
We look forward to serving you better. A very warm welcome to the larger Runwal Family! 


<br/><br/>
Best Regards,<br/>
<apex:outputText style="text-transform: capitalize" value="{!relatedTo.RW_Booking__r.RM_Name__c}"></apex:outputText><br/>
